revisions.description: Added new Distributed Services Module MIB
Added 6400 Rev C chassis OID information.
Updated with new SKU OIDs for Indy program
Updated with 6300M DC PSU OID information.
Updated with fixed PSU OID information.
Updated with JL762A new Product OID information.
Updated with JL687A new Product OID information.
Added new 8325 switches and updated description text for all 8325 switches
Made changes to move VSX MIB under new OID tree.
Added new 8320 switches and updated description text for all 8320 switches
Updated Aruba Wired MIB Object Names with a standard convention
